    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>beef stock</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the<strong> balsamic vinegar</strong> (save the rest for later!) with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Return the <strong>lean beef</strong> <strong>meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 6 min or until the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened</p><p>Meanwhile, drain your<strong> mozzarella </strong>and tear it into rough pieces</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
